      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just... they have their own lives to live, you know? their jobs, their families... i'm just an extra thing they have to manage. i look at them and i just feel so guilty. i feel like if i weren't here, they'd finally have the space to just... breathe and live without worrying about me every single day. wouldn't it be better for everyone if they didn't have to worry?",
